0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kbhSBKqn7AQ5hDoyeR-daA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FkbhSBKqn7AQ5hDoyeR-daA&d=EJiCHVrPimDYvebvO0lo5p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e91c5a89\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kbhSBKqn7AQ5hDoyeR-daA</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Sorry for quoting 殘體字<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>本文的最後說一下。上海乃是外資進入中國的橋頭堡，中國的外企總部聚集地。2017年上海利用外資規模170億美元，較峰值年份2016年的185億美元下降了8.1%。今年1季度這種下降趨勢在繼續，利用外資規模37億美元，較2017年同期減少2.2%。問題的關鍵在於，外資企業不再願意投資在上海的固定資產領域了。今年1季度上海的固定資產投資到位資金4088億，同比下降2.5%。引發下降的原因在於外企到位資金只有7千萬，同比降幅高達90.9%。對這組數據，我只能這麼評價：在上海的外企總部穿著全身阿瑪尼帶著假領子擠地鐵上班的高級金領們，很快就會體會到為他們所鄙視的衣著邋遢的碼農們每天晚上吃泡面的心情了。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n贏國在外資投入減少的情況下，或許刺激本地投資進入外資空白處，贏國或許又成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"71ec2b46e2420be638e16a899eb719512168385d","tid":668144,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔係歐盟唔俾賣俾支那咩?"},{"pid":"df7b82f59c1ea720ded1f5081f5e3d398d63936c","tid":668144,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ae963f1c99b628c5a7a27f553c1394e2f60e2f69","tid":668144,"uid":3508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e830f15cc58673e2477307347e335e9c7768d32","tid":668144,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"47f715f18b69669dd8f11e6003dc8d2ee88b4368","tid":668144,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"evu咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"之前控制唔到ga科技"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"水顯式做唔到7nm以下<br />\n要用evu先可以做到